{"tid":1516220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）懷疑家姐被黑客呃左資料","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:02:38.000Z","uid":182984,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a977e9f2874c3f3af01888bac796bef0fcc4debf","tid":1516220,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"事緣係我家姐收到一個email 註冊左新ig account（但佢一早用左呢個account申請）之後佢就上網搵facebook同埋ig既email去屌柒佢地 之後佢話第二日ig del撚左佢account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁佢又Send email去屌 點之email回覆佢叫佢證明身分（如圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wb44E0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwb44E0H.jpg&h=97f522c3&s={SIZE}\" />要upload身分證佢又傻下傻下咁冇懷疑就send左身份證 而家冇再覆佢email佢今日覺得好怪 而家搵左莫乃光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴絲知點做 因為而家報警搵狗都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要屌請屌細力啲 小妹愛姐心切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe8c982d6c7779f95acd7912ef0b13e3b047d24","tid":1516220,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"自推十下<br />\n1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7b7cfbee8e78fe79b088c2f8443713f5e6b7a6","tid":1516220,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"自推十下<br />\n2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f53b7a8762084a18edd44d339f87bc8c3e774af","tid":1516220,"uid":237372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"斷十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ab233b2751216196e5c9be59edb6df487880e0","tid":1516220,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0